ZH: 她的心肠真好，总是乐于助人。
EN: Her heart is kind, and she is always willing to help others.

ZH: 他是个心肠狠毒的人，绝不会轻易原谅别人。
EN: He is a person with a cruel heart who will never easily forgive others.

ZH: 她是个心肠软的人，很容易被感动。
EN: She is a person with a tender heart who is easily moved.

ZH: 我的妈妈有一颗善良的心肠。
EN: My mother has a kind heart.

ZH: 他有一颗温柔的心肠，总是对人和善。
EN: He has a gentle heart and is always kind to others.

ZH: 他认为自己是个心肠硬的人，很少向他人展现情感。
EN: He considers himself as a person with a tough heart and seldom shows emotions to others.

ZH: 她的心肠很大，总是愿意倾听别人的烦恼。
EN: She has a big heart and is always willing to listen to others' troubles.

ZH: 他在事业上是个心肠狠毒的人，不择手段地达到自己的目标。
EN: He is a person with a ruthless heart in his career, using any means to achieve his goals.

ZH: 做一个有爱心的人，拥有一颗善良的心肠。
EN: Be a caring person with a kind heart.

ZH: 她虽然性格高傲，但内心的心肠还是很善良的。
EN: Although she has a proud personality, her heart is still kind.

ZH: 我很幸运拥有一群心肠好的朋友。
EN: I am lucky to have a group of friends with good hearts.

ZH: 他内心的心肠很阴暗，总是想尽办法伤害别人。
EN: His heart is dark, always finding ways to hurt others.

ZH: 她内心的心肠很温暖，总是愿意给予他人关爱。
EN: Her heart is warm, always willing to give love to others.

ZH: 你的心肠真好，总是对人和善。
EN: Your heart is kind, always kind to others.

ZH: 我听说他的心肠很坏，所以要小心对待。
EN: I heard that he has a bad heart, so be careful when dealing with him.

ZH: 他的心肠很冷漠，从不关心别人的感受。
EN: He has a cold heart and never cares about others' feelings.

ZH: 她有一颗善变的心肠，经常改变自己的想法。
EN: She has a fickle heart and often changes her mind.

ZH: 我们应该培养一颗善良的心肠，用爱心对待他人。
EN: We should cultivate a kind heart and treat others with love.

ZH: 他的心肠残忍，从不心软。
EN: His heart is cruel and never soft.

ZH: 她的心肠张冠李戴，总是将事情想得太复杂。
EN: Her heart is complicated, always overthinking things.
